                    <span>I'm so grateful for Dr. Orloff's own positive energy and sharing of her wisdom and knowledge with all who read her work.  Her deep insight into how to transform our stressed out lives from the constant daily challenges we all encounter, into  wonderful, extraordinary and perhaps most importantly, healthy lives, has helped myself and so many of the people I hold dear and close to my heart. I have been so impressed by this book, that I have given it as a gift to almost everyone I know and recommend it to all of my patients families.  All have appreciated the practical down-to-earth tools that Dr. Orloff shares with  her warmth, humor and compassion.  You can see from so many loving reviews that have been posted how Dr. Orloff's work has touched the hearts of so many.  I only want to add another voice to that long list that says, Dr. Judith Orloff, thank you, thank you, thank you! Thank you for making the world a far more positive place  by sharing your truly extraordinary prescriptions for transformation with us. </span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A must read</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
